entries.abort: Haha, good luck finding Uff now!
entries.arrival_phase_1: Scanning pre programmed route for ship signature now.
entries.arrival_phase_2: Ship signature encountered. 99.8421% probability of correct ship.
entries.capture_complete: Tactical Computer: < Sensors indicate target vessel powering up. >
entries.capture_phase_1: Who the heck are you and what do you think you're doing?!
entries.capture_phase_2: Wogo you say? Fine, I'll take you to where I was supposed to meet him later.
entries.capture_started: Tactical Computer: < Sensors indicate target vessel disabled. >
entries.complete: You fool! You actually think I'd give up my friend to you? You filthy bounty hunter. Get him boys!
entries.failed_destroy: Sensors can no longer find previous target vessel.
entries.failed_escape: Sensors indicate target vessel initiated hyperdrive and can no longer be tracked.
entries.quest_disable_d: Your computer is tracking Ogveer's ship. Hunt him down and disable his engines.
entries.quest_escort_d: Escort Ogveer to where he was supposed to meet with Uff Wogo and await his arrival at that spot.
entries.quest_location_d: The Dantooine system is largely unknown but rumored to have a high population of pirates.
entries.quest_recover_d: Ogveer has agreed to lead you to where he's supposed to meet with Uff Wogo. Wait for him to fix the engines on his ship.
entries.recovery_success: Sensors indicate target vessel initiated hyperdrive and can no longer be tracked.
entries.target_disabled: Tactical Computer: < Sensors indicate power failure on target. >
entries.title: Dantooine system: Tracking down Ogveer.
entries.title_d: With the coordinates given to you by Kkrax, travel to the Dantooine system and scan the route for Ogveer.
